metadata.name: LazyLand
metadata.description:
This piece is dedicated to whoever is in a search of inspiration and productivity while feeling lazy in a black hole of no pupose, surrounded by many unwanted companions as a lonely sock, unwashed dishes and his glory, Morpheus the god of sleep & dreams.

Remember, your inner tiger is asleep but soon will wake up with a rawr!

High resolution 3543x2598 px
